---
layout: "base.njk"
title: "Representasjon"
loggedIn: true
pagination:
  data: agents
  size: 1
  alias: agent
permalink: "/{{ agent.name | slugify }}/representasjon/index.html"
---

<div class="container container--prose account-selection">
  <div class="page-crumbs"><a href="/{{ agents[0].name | slugify }}/minside/">Min side</a> /</div>
  <h1>{{ title }}</h1>

  <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Nam blanditiis obcaecati ratione, molestiae suscipit inventore error consequuntur ab non atque neque enim repellat, itaque placeat possimus. Quam molestiae iure neque!</p>

  <div class="agent-list">
    <h2>Velg hvem du skal representere</h2> 
    <ul>
      {%- for profile in agents %}
      <li>
        <a class="account-option" href="/{{ profile.name | slugify }}/minside/">
          <div class="avatar {{ 'avatar--main' if profile.type != 'agent' }}">
            {{ profile.icon | svgContents | safe }}
          </div>
          <div>
            <strong>{{ profile.name }}</strong>
            <small>{{ profile.role }}</small>
          </div>
          {% if loop.first %}<span class="tag">Deg</span>{% endif %}
        </a>
      </li>
      {%- endfor %}
    </ul>
  </div>

</div>
